701120f-a.title: Bronx: Goodridge Avenue - 250th Street (West)
701120f-a.text:
Goodridge Ave., at the N.W. corner of West 250th Street, showing
the home of Dwigght J. Baum, noted architect. It is within the restricted
residential section known as Fieldston.
About 1928.
Joseph P. Day.
CREDIT LINE IMPERATIVE ON ALL REPRODUCTIONS.
